nodes.text: Dokath-Ra was a male Voss Mystic during the Galactic War.

Dokath-Ra decided to help the Galactic Republic General Thelonia Redrish in her quest to pass the Mystic's Spirit Trial and for this Dokath ordered his apprentice Shajahm-Do to conducted to him a bounty hunter that the Sith Lord Darth Tormen send after Thelonia. But when Dokath met the Hunter he couldn't convince them to rest in peace so a fight erupted and the Hunter killed Dokath and all the other pro-Republic mystics before they restart the hunt for Thelonia.
